pageContext.description: Length: 104.5mm; width mouth 41.5mm; width edge 49.5mm; width loop 9.8mm; breadth mouth 40mm; depth socket 63mm,One face - five evenly spaced ribs plus emphasised body angles, reverse - six ribs plus emphasised body angles; parts of fine casting flash on sides; slight blade tip hollows; small pit beside loop - casting flaw; narrow rectangular socket end; spaced double mask moulding.
pageContext.patina: V. little dark green patina; mainly observed by granular light green surfaces.
pageContext.surface: Edge mainly intact and sharp; small chip revealing coppery brown probably recent, as also odd patches on body. Light orange-brown soil adhering.
